Attribution
-----------
Attribution is appreciated for code (MIT) and required for documentation
(CC BY 4.0). A reasonable attribution looks like:

    Portions adapted from "Awesome React Native Agent Skills"
    (https://github.com/<your-handle>/awesome-react-native-agent-skills),
    licensed under MIT and CC BY 4.0.

Questions about licensing can be opened as an issue on the repository.
